name: Autotroph (foldings)
description: Video feedback as a self perpetuating visual system | A simple square is sent around a loop of renderers with transformations along the way creating transformations of transformations ad infinitum. Now in colour for the first time → Autotroph (from the Greek autos = self and trophe = nutrition). Artwork by Paul Prudence @MrPrudence → 4k PNG, 2021
